d in the Welcome Package.</font></div><div><br></div><div><font face="arial">We look forward to working with you and strengthening our relationship in the coming years. Should you have any questions, please don’t hesitate to contact any of the team members.&nbsp;</font></div><div><br></div><div><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Justin</font></div><div><br></div><div><font face="arial">Justin Monge&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial">Senior Vice President&nbsp;</font></div><div><br></div><div><font face="arial">Brookfield Real Estate Financial Partners LLC&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial">T (212)-417-7288</font></div>]]></td>
